Bioscope Factory arrives on 27th October with its next workshop on
Direction S01E01: Technical tabs of Film Making
Time: 6 PM
Venue: Loading...

Writer writes. Cinematographer shoots. Actors act. Editor edits. So what
the Director does?
If you are wondering what does a director of a film really do,
let us break it down for you in-da-workshop, da!

At the workshop, from director's POV we will explore:

   - Process of film-making: pre-production, production, and post-productio=
n
   - Area of work
   - Tools of work
   - Know hows of directing a film before you decide to do so.

Requirements for the workshop: Sketch Pens

